    "body": "Also this is a big issue when having dogs or civilians in an inf group: certain tragets cant be attacked and the otehr soldiers in the group then do nothing if ordered - which is very, very agitating in an important attack.\n\nA dirty fix would be to give those units a secondary attack that can target air,buildings and so on, which has a certain range and _no damage_.  For the engi this would target infantry, tanks and air.\n"
